      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.304</ph> Small disadvantaged
business status.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1146e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1175e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The contracting officer may accept
an offeror’s representation that it is a small disadvantaged business
concern (SDB) concern.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1175e15" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The provision
at <xref href="52.219-1.dita#FAR_52_219_1"
                        base="i1057235"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-1</xref>, Small Business
Program Representations, or <xref href="52.212-3.dita#FAR_52_212_3"
                        base="i1060550"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.212-3</xref>(c)(4),
Offeror Representations and <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>Certifications-Commercial
Products and <?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 19.304 by removing from paragraph (b) the term “Certifications—Commercial Items” and adding “Certifications—Commercial Products and Commercial Services” in its place.?>Commercial Services,</ph> is used to collect SDB data.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1175e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> A representation
of SDB status on a Federal prime contract will be deemed a misrepresentation
of SDB status if the firm does not meet the requirements of <ph outputclass="CFR" class="- topic/ph ">13 CFR 124.1001(b)</ph>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1175e40" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> Any person
or entity that misrepresents a firm's status as an SDB concern in
order to obtain a contracting opportunity in accordance with section
8(d) of the Small Business Act, (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref "> 15 U.S.C. 637(d)</xref>)
will be subject to the penalties imposed by section 16(d) of the
Small Business Act, (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15 U.S.C. 645(d)</xref>),
as well as any other penalty authorized by law.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
